Welcome to Quartzsite Elementary School District #4
Inspiring and Motivating student’s success through Education
Our goal is to partner with students, staff, parents, community and board members to create an environment where all students are empowered to discover and achieve their maximum potential.
Learn about our history and values

The 2019-2020 school year promises to be an incredible year! On behalf of the District Board of Education and the entire staff, I extend a warm welcome to our district families. As I enter my fourth year serving as Superintendent and eighteenth year in the district, I continue to cherish the opportunities that allow me to connect with and support our students, parents, and staff. I consider it a privilege to serve this district and communities. We have a dedicated Board of Education, talented staff, and outstanding students!

QSD#4 remains committed to continuous improvement at our exceptional schools. We are continuously updating our safety and security measures with a focus on emergency communication, secure facilities, and options-based emergency preparedness plans. Our schools will be undergoing improvements this year. Our teachers have been busy throughout the summer preparing for the new school year

QSD#4 strives to create a community that craves learning, fosters resiliency, and cares deeply for every child. We are committed to providing the best possible educational experience for all students. I invite each of you to stay connected and involved in your child’s education. Together we can look forward to seeing our children achieve, succeed, and grow!
Due to COVID-19 all Arizona Schools are closed through end of school year 2019-2020
